data.value:
This tool measures the overall mood of the crypto market using real-time data.
It ranges from 0 (Extreme Fear) to 100 (Extreme Greed): - Fear means investors are worried — could signal a buying opportunity. - Greed means high confidence or hype — be cautious of overbought conditions.
Our sentiment reading helps you understand how the crowd feels — so you can trade smarter.
